		<div id="post-2360" class="cf post-2360 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

			<h1>
				<a href="http://werblog.com/2012/03/twitter-updates-for-2012-03-02/" title="Twitter Updates for 2012-03-02" rel="bookmark">Twitter Updates for 2012-03-02</a>
				
			</h1>

			<div class="post-footer">
				2 Mar 2012 &nbsp;&nbsp;| <a href="http://werblog.com/category/uncategorized/">Uncategorized</a>
				
			</div>

			<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
				<ul class="aktt_tweet_digest">
<li>Help my brother reach a milestone!  RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/adamwerbach" class="aktt_username">adamwerbach</a>: I&#039;m 3 followers away from 10,000, thanks to your FF# today.  Thank you! <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175612484164661249" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>I took The Anti-Corruption Pledge, have you? <a href="http://t.co/ahuzS7Yv" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/ahuzS7Yv</a> #<a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23takethepledge" class="aktt_hashtag">takethepledge</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175613847367991296" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>@<a href="http://twitter.com/marvin_ammori" class="aktt_username">marvin_ammori</a> on online video innovation and TV broadcasters&#039; lawsuit against Aereo: <a href="http://t.co/weptghTZ" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/weptghTZ</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175615860411600898" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>I love that @<a href="http://twitter.com/marvin_ammori" class="aktt_username">marvin_ammori</a> had to explain the diff b/t broadcast and cable. Shows how outdated these rules are! <a href="http://t.co/weptghTZ" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/weptghTZ</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175616171519905795" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>@<a href="http://twitter.com/martingeddes" class="aktt_username">martingeddes</a> In the US, the constant need for money is what corrupts the system.  No one else has multi-billion dollar elections! <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175616638916366338" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>@<a href="http://twitter.com/marvin_ammori" class="aktt_username">marvin_ammori</a> Dunno, we don&#039;t offer &quot;broadcast law&quot; for our MBAs. It&#039;s more amazing that law students would take that course and not know! <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175616847905964032" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Why the &quot;but&quot;?   The Economist: “&#039;Gamification&#039; is an ugly word, but it sounds like money to some.&quot; <a href="http://t.co/xTC0GlV9" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/xTC0GlV9</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175617908095991808" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/hermanwagter" class="aktt_username">hermanwagter</a>: Freedom To Connect is back! May 21-22 Washington, DC. Vint Cerf, @<a href="http://twitter.com/doctorow" class="aktt_username">doctorow</a> @rmack, and many more <a href="http://t.co/KVhiBfyB" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/KVhiBfyB</a> #<a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23f2c" class="aktt_hashtag">f2c</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175622244830154752" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>IP lawyers gone wild. Louis Vuitton sent a bogus cease &amp; desist letter to Penn Law for this conference poster: <a href="http://t.co/Y2xzqYIC" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/Y2xzqYIC</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175637252947456000" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>@<a href="http://twitter.com/derekslater" class="aktt_username">derekslater</a> I don&#039;t have the cease &amp; desist letter.  Ask Polk Wagner or Shyam Balganesh at Penn Law, who are leading the response. <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175638624258363393" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Fortunately, Penn has top-tier IP law scholars and in-house counsel, who all agree the Fashion Law poster is not infringing. <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175639064689647618" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Pu-erh: It&#039;s the coffee of teas. <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175641486489169920" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Go Liz Go!!! MT @<a href="http://twitter.com/reneehobbs" class="aktt_username">reneehobbs</a>: RIT&#039;s Liz Lawley: developing mastery through game play w/ freshman #<a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23dml2012" class="aktt_hashtag">dml2012</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175642126812577792" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/jhagel" class="aktt_username">jhagel</a>: &quot;Serendipity is too important to be left to chance&quot; &#8211; Yossi Vardi, standing in a hallway during a session at #<a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23TED2012" class="aktt_hashtag">TED2012</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175642697439256577" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Well, AT&amp;T&#039;s cable assets were bought by Comcast, so&#8230;   RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/ericries" class="aktt_username">ericries</a>: Who is the &quot;AT&amp;T of cable&quot;? <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175653611047632897" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/dajbconf" class="aktt_username">dajbconf</a>: DML launching &#039;Spigot&#039; an hub for aggregating news, research, opinion and info: <a href="http://t.co/CPhttp://spigot.org" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/CPhttp://spigot.org</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175660015535915009" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>The *last*? RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/CathyNDavidson" class="aktt_username">CathyNDavidson</a>: &quot;Education is last arena in which technology is seriously underleveraged.&quot;- @<a href="http://twitter.com/mkapor" class="aktt_username">mkapor</a> #<a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23dml2012" class="aktt_hashtag">dml2012</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175666120513167360" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
<li>Wonder if he&#039;s going to change his mind?  RT @<a href="http://twitter.com/kevinrose" class="aktt_username">kevinrose</a>: brett favre has joined twitter! @<a href="http://twitter.com/BrettFavre4" class="aktt_username">BrettFavre4</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/175698332251996160" class="aktt_tweet_time">#</a></li>
</ul>

				
			</div>

			
			


